<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.8.5">
<l>kalaikaḷum vētamum nītinūluṅ kaṟpamuñ coṟporuḷ tāṉumaṟṟai</l>
<l>nilaikaḷum vāṉavark kumpiṟarkkum nīrmaiyi ṉālaruḷ ceytunīṇṭa</l>
<l>malaikaḷum māmaṇi yummalarmēl maṅkaiyuñ caṅkamum taṅkukiṉṟa</l>
<l>valaikaṭal pōṉṟiva rārkkoleṉṉa vaṭṭapu yakarat tēṉeṉṟārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I asked, “Who is this appearing [like] the crashing sea</l>
<l>In which high mountains, a great jewel, the lady on the blossom,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the conch are abiding,</l>
<l>Kindly bestowing the arts, the Vedas, the legal treatises, the Kalpa [Sutra],</l>
<l rend="indent">the meaning of words,</l>
<l>And other practices for the celestials and for others?”</l>
<l rend="indent">he answered, “I am he in the house of the eight-armed [lord].”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
